88 template < typename Type >
89 class Vector2
90 {
91 public:
92  Type x;
93  Type y;
94 
95 public:
96  bool operator== (const Vector2 & _Vector) const
97  {
98  if (x != _Vector.x) return false;
99  if (y != _Vector.y) return false;
100  return true;
101  }
102 
103 public:
104  Vector2(void) {}
105  Vector2(Type _X, Type _Y) : x(_X), y(_Y) {}
106 };
